sub_title: Project manager Communications, Training and Coaching, Conferences, Dutch, English and Swedish
summary:
Available, B2B Communication - Project manager Communications - Training & Coaching - Conferences - Translations

23 years of experience as project manager communications 
Projectmanager
• set up and managed an large number of working groups
• organised 60 conferences with 100-500 participants
• organised several national evaluations
• projects on location: 
   - organising and recording of several instructional videos in the Netherlands
   - organising and recording of crashtest in Germany

Developing communication products
• presentations
• reports
• manuals
• guidelines
• apps
• instruction videos
• websites

Developing training and instruction materials
• e-learning
• instruction videos
• three nationwide training programs for the Ministry of Infrastructure and Water Management
• three training programs for international delegations

Training and coaching
• training of individuals and groups
• training of the trainers for the nationwide training of 60.000 Incident Management emergency responders

Assignments from the government, companies and educational institutions

Social compentence; entrepreneurial qualities; analytical capabilities; decisive; reliable

Focus on high quality and customer satisfaction; communicative skills; problem solving skills

Dutch, English, Swedish and French
